 (41,'Lamborghini','Estoque','Sedan','<TEXTFORMAT LEADING=\"2\"><P ALIGN=\"LEFT\"><FONT  SIZE=\"16\"  LETTERSPACING=\"0\" KERNING=\"0\">The Estoque establishes a new category of super sports sedans. With a powerful front mid-engine, permanent all-wheel drive and a sophisticated, precision-tuned chassis, the Estoque boasts a unique technology package. Estoque embodies the concept of a Lamborghini that is both a dedicated sports car and a relaxed Gran Turismo. As a sedan with four doors and four individual sports seats, it is a multi-faceted vehicle for multi-faceted lifestyles.</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT><TEXTFORMAT LEADING=\"2\"><P ALIGN=\"LEFT\"><FONT  SIZE=\"16\"  LETTERSPACING=\"0\" KERNING=\"0\">Of course, as a true Lamborghini, it goes without saying that the Estoque also bears a suitably powerful name with a rich heritage from the Spanish Corrida -bull fighting. The Estoque is a rapier (sword), approximately 90 centimetres(35.43 inches) long, used in a bull fight by the Matador.</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT><TEXTFORMAT LEADING=\"2\"><P ALIGN=\"LEFT\"><FONT  SIZE=\"16\"  LETTERSPACING=\"0\" KERNING=\"0\">At the end of the day, it is the only car that allows you to share the singular driving pleasure of a Lamborghini with more than one person - possibly even with the whole family. And there is still enough room left over for weekend luggage or several golf bags. </FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>','http://content.hphantdev.com/temp/video/lambo/estoque/estoque1_lamb_397x280_pad.flv,http://content.hphantdev.com/temp/video/lambo/estoque/estoque2_unveiling_bmcd_lamb_420x238_pad.flv,http://content.hphantdev.com/temp/video/lambo/estoque/estoque3_ceo_english_bmcd_lamb_238x321_pad_16x9.flv','http://content.hphantdev.com/temp/images/lambo/estoque/estoque_01.png,http://content.hphantdev.com/temp/images/lambo/estoque/estoque_02.png,http://content.hphantdev.com/temp/images/lambo/estoque/estoque_03.png,http://content.hphantdev.com/temp/images/lambo/estoque/estoque_04.png,http://content.hphantde